OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1776517870
OL,3,CWoman banned from entering every Co-op
OL,4,Cstore in Kent for two years
OL,6,FWatch: Shannon Rossiter caught on CCTV
OL,7,Fstealing products
OL,9,FA woman branded a serial shoplifter by
OL,10,Fpolice who assaulted staff when
OL,11,Fchallenged has been banned from
OL,12,Fentering any Co-op store in Kent for
OL,13,Fthe next two years.
OL,15,FShannon Rossiter entered multiple
OL,16,Fshops over a two year period, filled
OL,17,Fup baskets with products and left
OL,18,Fwithout paying.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/7
