CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1776517870
OL,3,CWoman banned from entering every Co-op
OL,4,Cstore in Kent for two years
OL,6,FOn 14 October 2025, at around 8pm,
OL,7,FRossiter went into the Coop in
OL,8,FSturry, selecting various cleaning
OL,9,Fproducts and cans of alcohol before
OL,10,Fplacing them into a basket.
OL,12,FA staff member, suspicious of her
OL,13,Fbehaviour, watched as she headed
OL,14,Ftoward the exit without attempting to
OL,15,Fpay.
OL,17,FThe doors were closed to prevent her
OL,18,Fleaving, but when staff tried to
OL,19,Frecover the items, Rossiter became
OL,20,Fviolent and assaulted two employees
OL,21,Fbefore fleeing.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
