CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1776517870
OL,3,CWoman banned from entering every Co-op
OL,4,Cstore in Kent for two years
OL,6,FThe store suffered a loss of #88.
OL,8,FA month earlier, she stole four
OL,9,Fsandwiches worth #13 from Tesco in
OL,10,FSturry.
OL,12,FOn 2nd November, she took alcoholic
OL,13,Fdrinks worth #11.80 from the Coop in
OL,14,FWhitstable, then returned the next day
OL,15,Fand stole more food and drink worth
OL,16,F#15.35.
OL,18,FHer arrest came on 16th November after
OL,19,Fshe stole four gift sets valued at
OL,20,F#222 from Boots in Canterbury.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
