CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1776517870
OL,3,CWoman banned from entering every Co-op
OL,4,Cstore in Kent for two years
OL,6,FOfficers found her shortly after in a
OL,7,FWaitrose car park, recovering one gift
OL,8,Fset from her and three hidden nearby.
OL,10,FAfter appearing in court, Rossiter
OL,11,Fplead guilty to five counts of theft
OL,12,Fcommitted over a twomonth period.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
