PN,41205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1776517870
OL,3,CWoman banned from entering every Co-op
OL,4,Cstore in Kent for two years
OL,6,FThe prolific thief has now been handed
OL,7,Fa two-year Criminal Behaviour Order
OL,8,Fwhich prohibit her from entering any
OL,9,Fshop owned, run or managed by
OL,10,FCoOperative Retail Services Ltd
OL,11,Fwithin Kent for the next two years.
OL,12,FShe is also banned from entering any
OL,13,Fretail premises in the company of
OL,14,Fseveral named individuals.
OL,16,FCanterbury Inspector Daniel Fordom
OL,17,Fsaid:
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
