PN,41206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1776517870
OL,3,CWoman banned from entering every Co-op
OL,4,Cstore in Kent for two years
OL,6,F"Whilst Rossiter did not receive a
OL,7,Fcustodial sentence, the detailed
OL,8,Faccounts provided by staff and the
OL,9,Fevidence gathered by officers were
OL,10,Fcrucial in securing this long-term CBO.
OL,12,F"It sends a clear message that
OL,13,Fsustained and violent shoplifting will
OL,14,Fnot be tolerated, and we will continue
OL,15,Fto work closely with retailers and the
OL,16,Fcourt system to secure more orders
OL,17,Flike this one."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/7
